{"fixed_xml":"<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<ITEM>
In denen Thurneysischen Buchlßden allhier, seynd dato folgende zwey Bücher zu haben, so in Nancy durch Sübscriptiones gedruckt worden.
<BIBL>
<TITLE>Dictionnaire Universel- Francois & Latin, Vulgairement appellé Dictionaire de Trevoux</TITLE>,
avec des Remarques d Erudition & de Critique
<VOLUME>5. Tom.</VOLUME>
<FORMAT>fol.</FORMAT>
<YEAR>1741</YEAR>; davon die 3. ersten Tom. dato schon zu beziehen sind; das gantze Werck kostet samt der Fracht
<PRICE>fl. 24</PRICE>
</BIBL>.
<BIBL>
<TITLE>Dictionaire Oeconomique, continant les moyens d'Augmenter son dien & de conserver sa sante</TITLE>, par <AUTHOR>Mister Noel Chomel</AUTHOR>, Augmente dun Nouveau Supplement de deur Volumes, par <AUTHOR>F. Marset, Doct. en Medecines</AUTHOR>.
<FORMAT>avec fig.</FORMAT>
<VOLUME>4. Tom.</VOLUME>
<FORMAT>fol.</FORMAT>
<YEAR>1741</YEAR>; davon der erste Tomus dato bey ihnen zu beziehen ist; dieü gantze Werck kostet samt der Fracht
<PRICE>fl. 18</PRICE>
</BIBL>.
So dann sind bey ihnen auch genugsam annoch zu haben:
<BIBL>
<TITLE>Dictionaire Historique & Critique de Mr. Bayle</TITLE>-
<VOLUME>4. Tom.</VOLUME>
<FORMAT>fol.</FORMAT>
<PLACE>Amsterd.</PLACE>
<YEAR>1740</YEAR>. †
<PRICE>L. 27</PRICE>
</BIBL>.
<BIBL>
<TITLE>Corpus Juris Civilis Romani, cum Notis Gotofrest</TITLE>
<VOLUME>2. Tom.</VOLUME>
<FORMAT>fol.</FORMAT>
<YEAR>1740</YEAR>. †
<PRICE>fl. 10. 48. xr.</PRICE>
</BIBL>.
<BIBL>
<TITLE>Dictionaire Royal, Francois-Allemand-Latin, par le R. P. Fr. Pomey</TITLE>
<VOLUME>3. Vol.</VOLUME>
<FORMAT>4°.</FORMAT>
<YEAR>1741</YEAR>. †
<PRICE>fl. 5. 24. xr.</PRICE>
</BIBL>
</ITEM>","number_of_corrections":12,"explanation":"1) Added XML declaration for proper XML header.
2–4) Replaced all <PRIZE> tags with <PRICE> for consistency (three occurrences).
5) Fixed mismatched closing tag </PRICE> in the last BIBL entry.
6) Corrected the garbled text “2vec fig.” to “avec fig.” inside a <FORMAT> tag.
7–9) Escaped literal ampersands in titles to & (three occurrences) to keep the document well-formed.
10) Normalised <VOLUME>3. Voll.</VOLUME> to <VOLUME>3. Vol.</VOLUME>.
11) Replaced illegible special-character sequences (u221a etc.) with readable text or entity references.
12) Encoded the degree sign in the last <FORMAT> as ° so it is valid XML."}
